8.1 WARRANTY

Supplier warrants that all Goods delivered under this Purchase Order:

    (a) Conform to all specifications, drawings, samples, and
        descriptions applicable to this Purchase Order;
    (b) Are free from defects in materials and workmanship;
    (c) Are free from defects in design to the extent Supplier is
        responsible for design;
    (d) Are merchantable and fit for their intended purpose;
    (e) Are manufactured using new materials only, unless otherwise
        authorized in writing;
    (f) Do not infringe any patent, trademark, copyright, or other
        intellectual property right of any third party.

This warranty shall remain in effect for the later of: (i) thirty-six
(36) months from Buyer's acceptance, or (ii) twenty-four (24) months
from installation in the end item aircraft.

8.3 INDEMNIFICATION

Supplier shall indemnify, defend, and hold harmless Buyer, its
customers, and the Government from and against all claims, damages,
losses, costs, and expenses (including reasonable attorney's fees)
arising from:

    (a) Any breach of Supplier's warranties;
    (b) Any defect in the Goods;
    (c) Any negligent act or omission of Supplier;
    (d) Any infringement of intellectual property rights;
    (e) Any violation of applicable laws or regulations.
